      <Commentary>
         <ab>Y4.3a <bibl>Kellens, 1996</bibl>, p. 58 suggests the elimination of the first <em>gąmca huδā̊ŋhəm</em> (cf. Y3.1-4).</ab>
         <ab>Y4.3b <em>aṣ̌aiiąmca</em>] sec, Redard; Geldner <em>aš́iiąmca</em>; Kellens em. <em>⁺aṣ̌aiiąmca</em>.</ab>
         <ab>Y4.3b <em>ratufritīmca</em>] vid. Y3.4.</ab>
      </Commentary>
      <RecitationInstruction>
         <ab><em>āat̰ dīš āuuaēδaiiamahi ima humatāca ...</em>] <em>āat̰ aimahumatāica</em> tāsra <em>āat̰</em> (Y4.4) 231.</ab>
      </RecitationInstruction>
   </Apparatus>
   <Parallels>
