    </Parallels>
   <Ritual>
   <Nerangs id="ritualNerangs">
      <ab>Y4.3 (mss. 4010, 4020, 4025, 4030, 4040, 4045, 4050, 4055, 4060, 4063, 4161, 4162): </ab>
      <ab class="ab_indent">
         bōy ō ī ātaxš dō bār dahišn <em>āat̰.dīš āuuaēδaiiamahi ima humatāca huxtāca huuarštāca</em> ...</ab>
      <ab class="ab_indent">
         "He has to give <em>bōy</em> to the fire twice at <em>āat̰.dīš āuuaēδaiiamahi ima humatāca huxtāca huuarštāca</em>..."</ab>
   </Nerangs>
